footer.text: Character Guide • Synergy: Nilou | Update Date: 10/14/2022 | Editor: Samantha#9907

fields.name: Notes:
fields.value:
Due to her Passives and the nature of her kit it is highly recommended to play her with only Hydro and Dendro teammates. 
There are currently a limited number of Dendro characters at this time, so expect updates as more characters are released!
